						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Śaka 1547 (1626 A.D.)</hi></p>						

						<p>Seems to record an endowment, the details of which are not clear. The details of the date viz., <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1547, Kshaya, Kārttigai 15, Vṛiśchika, śu. 5, Tuesday, Tiruvōṇam</hi> correspond to <hi rend="bold">1626 A.D., November 14, Tuesday, ·11, ·82 The Śaka year quoted is wrong for 1548.</hi></p>						

